text: Willi Welt (born 19 August 1926) was an Austrian gymnast. He competed at the 1948 Summer Olympics and the 1952 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1926 births Category:Possibly living people Category:Austrian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Austria Category:Gymnasts at the 1948 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
